Dear Judge Cott, 
Attached for the Court's consideration, please find two applications for search warrants and the corresponding proposed 
warrants. The agent will be available tomorrow to swear out both warrants, and I am available to answer any questions 
that may arise. I can be reached at my desk on my cellphone or by email at this address. 
Respectfully submitted, 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
1  St. Andrew's Plaza 
10007
